iragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, 'lucida sans regular', 'lucida sans unicode', arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34); line-height: 1.8em;\">Writing: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Gingerly\" target=\"_blank\">Gingerly</a><br />\n\tGingerly means extremely carefully. What is done gingerly? Why is the action done that way? What is the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They proceeded gingerly... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) approach the podium gingerly<br />\n\t2) gauging the crowd gingerly<br />\n\t3) walking on the frozen lake gingerly<br />\n\t4) handling artifacts gingerly<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAt first, the pair walked gingerly, learning the feel for the height and distance of each step as well as the balancing point for the two boxes. This was something one would not pay too much attention to if one could see clearly the path in front. The pair also kept a bit of distance between themselves, in case the person in the front slipped. After a couple flight of stairs, the task of carrying the boxes and walking up the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stairway\" target=\"_blank\">stairway</a> became a lot easier, at least that was what Shawn felt.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167385617902/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774872/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774872\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p741734/\">囧研究：人为什么会感到孤独？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775703/\">biscuit不是饼干！猜猜是什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775770/\">空中之城：高空拍摄下的迪拜美如画</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773174/\">20年前追星VS现在追星：节操是啥 能吃么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773543/\">涨知识：18个关于英语的冷知识 你知道吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776317/\">不知道查令街84号你看什么不二情书？！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775134/\">BBC模仿秀: 跑出悲恸</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775034/\">关于“烤”的三种表达：歪果仁教你花样下厨</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776306/\">解放军新征兵视频燃破天际：外媒都看呆了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776225/\">全球最值得一去主题公园TOP9：中国就占俩</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"marg